{"tid":2208742,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都係屙爛屎就會爆瘡","createTime":"2020-09-19T06:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T08:00:32.000Z","uid":149402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2905e69d6eeec1f062ae3cca55036c60a8d4e6bb","tid":2208742,"uid":149402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T06:58:18.000Z","msg":"前排唔知點解屙親屎都係爛屎 咁岩個排又係咁爆瘡<br />\n<br />\n跟住上兩個禮拜屙番正常屎之後皮膚就好番啲冇乜再點生暗瘡<br />\n<br />\n但呢幾日又屙番爛屎就又生左幾粒瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想知有冇其他人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c085006386208f8764f583a268713765d1c2e35","tid":2208742,"uid":149402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780be77668a97836e54dfcb52f72953089071b07","tid":2208742,"uid":370467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:06:51.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edaffa6f12cb442bdfc54942b6d1fb7f84ebec1","tid":2208742,"uid":149402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"780be77668a97836e54dfcb52f72953089071b07","tid":2208742,"uid":370467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:06:51.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgm